{
  "stem": "19921.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 142.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And the town was by the name of Chorzow, which was approximately 3 and 1/2 kilometer from the German border.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And I was living and apprenticing with him till the last day of, of August, when the war broke out in September 1st, 1939.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "I was apprenticing and living with him there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I was aware.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was aware for-- by-- for one thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was aware.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was aware also in upper Silesia, because, like, half a year before, there was half of-- in our city, which was Chorzow, half of the population was German, and half of the population was Polish.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, there were German, German Jews, and Poles, and Polish Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "To living-- to living there, because it was a border town, you need a special permit.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I had to have a special permit to live there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In any event, about half a year before the war started, I saw myself in our city-- that's the first time which I saw anti-Semitism really spring out.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Every Jewish store-- we woke up one morning, and every Jewish store had a sign on the window.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Not a sign-- you know, with the-- with the-- black whatever had-- they had.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Paint, or whatever they had or they were using that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know exactly what.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was strictly-- you know, it was a Jewish store.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was written [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That means Jew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then it was-- they had also different signs like, don't buy-- don't buy by Jew.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Buy by your own.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They didn't say Pole or German, because they couldn't.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So they'd just say, just buy by your own.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That was the first thing which I saw real antisemitism in the town.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
